creator: Nerdren
descriptionHtml:
Enemies are coming from all directions!
In this case, hit many enemies with lightning!

A very powerful monster appeared?
Then, let's stop the movement of monsters to the black hole!
■ Dungeon of magic
You can learn magic skills in Magic Dungeon. Make your own strategies with a variety of magic!

■ Let's grow into the gold we won in the dungeon
You can strengthen your skills with gold that you get from exploring dungeons. Don't you feel proud to see yourself surviving longer as you grow up?

■ A suspicious merchant in the dungeon?
If you explore the dungeon, you'll find someone wearing a mystic robe. Buy various magic items from him and learn powerful magic recipes! Of course, it's not free.

■ So many adventurers!
From Skull, a skeleton soldier who decided to become an adventurer in the Monster, to Cindy, a wizard who uses the power of spirits to use the magic of nature! There are many adventurers full of charm and personality!

■ Unlock your potential!
Soulstone, a mysterious gem, has a mystical power that maximizes your inner strength! Unlocking your potential with a soul stone allows you to use stronger magic!

Music used in the game : https://www.youtube.com/user/soundholick

You can learn magic skills in Magic Dungeon. Make your own strategies with a variety of magic!

■ Let's grow into the gold we won in the dungeon
You can strengthen your skills with gold that you get from exploring dungeons. Don't you feel proud to see yourself surviving longer as you grow up?

■ A suspicious merchant in the dungeon?
If you explore the dungeon, you'll find someone wearing a mystic robe. Buy various magic items from him and learn powerful magic recipes! Of course, it's not free.

■ So many adventurers!
From Skull, a skeleton soldier who decided to become an adventurer in the Monster, to Cindy, a wizard who uses the power of spirits to use the magic of nature! There are many adventurers full of charm and personality!
